    "updated_at": "2016-06-27T01:47:18Z",
    "body": "> Quote: The problem is page A don't received any messages from main.js\n\nIn main process:\n\n``` javascript\nvar ipcMain = require('electron').ipcMain;\n```\n\nIn renderer process\n\n``` javascript\nvar ipcRenderer = require('electron').ipcRenderer;\n```\n\nPlease take a look again at the official documentation:\n- [**ipcMain**](http://electron.atom.io/docs/api/ipc-main/)\n- [**ipcRenderer**](http://electron.atom.io/docs/api/ipc-renderer/)\n\nOr you can try to search further discussion about this at [**Stack Overflow**](http://stackoverflow.com/search?q=electron)\n"
